---
title: "Just nu"
layout: base.njk
templateClass: post-template
type: page
description: "Detta är en sida som visar vad jag hittar på just nu."
permalink: /just-nu/
eleventyComputed:
    meta:
        author:
            name: "{{ metadata.author.name }}"
    published: "{{ date }}"
    modified: "{% if updateDate %}{{ updateDate | iso8601 }}{% endif %}"
---
<article class="page">
    <header id="page-header" class="page-header">
        <div class="page-metadata">
            <h1 class="page-title">{{ title }}</h1>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section aria-label="Sidans innehåll" class="page-content content" id="page-content">
        <p class="lead">Detta är <a href="https://nownownow.com/about">en sida som visar vad jag hittar på just nu</a>. Vill du läsa mer om min bakgrund så kan du läsa
            <a href="/om-mig">om mig</a>.</p>
        <ul class="-no-style">
            <li>🏢 Jag bor i Jönköping och jobbar som webbutvecklare på <a href="https://ju.se/bibliotek">Högskolebiblioteket i Jönköping</a>.</li>
            <li>🏕️ Just nu planerar jag sommarens utflykter</li>
            {% if strava.activities.length %}{% for activity in strava.activities %}{% if loop.index0 < 1 %}
                {% if activity.type === 'Ride' %}<li>🚴 <a href="https://www.strava.com/activities/{{ activity.id }}">Jag cyklade {% if activity.distance_km %} <span class="activity-distance">{{ activity.distance_km | dotToComma }}km</span>{% endif %} <time class="timeago" datetime="{{ activity.start_date | fullISODate }}" title="{{ activity.start_date | longISODate }}">{{ activity.start_date | readableDate }}</time></a></li>{% endif %}
                {% if activity.type === 'Run' %}<li>🏃‍ <a href="https://www.strava.com/activities/{{ activity.id }}">Jag sprang {% if activity.distance_km %} <span class="activity-distance">{{ activity.distance_km | dotToComma }}km</span>{% endif %} <time class="timeago" datetime="{{ activity.start_date | fullISODate }}" title="{{ activity.start_date | longISODate }}">{{ activity.start_date | readableDate }}</time></a></li>{% endif %}
                {% if activity.type === 'Walk' %}<li>🚶‍ <a href="https://www.strava.com/activities/{{ activity.id }}">Jag gick {% if activity.distance_km %} <span class="activity-distance">{{ activity.distance_km | dotToComma }}km</span>{% endif %} <time class="timeago" datetime="{{ activity.start_date | fullISODate }}" title="{{ activity.start_date | longISODate }}">{{ activity.start_date | readableDate }}</time></a></li>{% endif %}
                {% if activity.type === 'Hike' %}<li>🚶‍🎒 <a href="https://www.strava.com/activities/{{ activity.id }}">Jag vandrade {% if activity.distance_km %} <span class="activity-distance">{{ activity.distance_km | dotToComma }}km</span>{% endif %} <time class="timeago" datetime="{{ activity.start_date | fullISODate }}" title="{{ activity.start_date | longISODate }}">{{ activity.start_date | readableDate }}</time></a></li>{% endif %}
            {% endif %}{% endfor %}{% endif %}
            {% if steam.recently_played_games.length %}<li>🎮 Jag spelar {% for game in steam.recently_played_games %}<a id="{{ game.appid }}" href="{{ game.url }}">{{ game.name }}</a>{% if loop.index0 < steam.recently_played_games.length - 2 %}, {% endif %}{% if loop.index0 == steam.recently_played_games.length - 2 %} och {% endif %}{% endfor %}</li>{% endif %}
            {% if goodreads.currently_reading.length %}{% if goodreads.currently_reading.length %}<li>📚 Jag läser {% for book in goodreads.currently_reading %}<a id="{{ book.book_id }}" href="{{ book.url }}"><em>{{ book.title }}</em></a> av {{ book.author }}{% if loop.index0 < goodreads.currently_reading.length - 2 %}, {% endif %}{% if loop.index0 == goodreads.currently_reading.length - 2 %} och {% endif %}{% endfor %}</li>
            {% endif %}{% endif %}
        </ul>
    </section>
</article>
